extends ./amc.amtee.layout.jade

block title
  title Event

block content
  .wrapper
    .poster#poster-label
      .ps-img
        //- Replace this with the poster image found in your images/amc.amtee folder.
        img(src="../../img/15-16/amc.amtee/poster.photo.jpg")
        .ps-cover
    .ps-well
      .col-md-3
      .col-md-6
        h1 AMTee会服设计比赛
        //h3 Exam Welfare Refreshment @ NTU
        .btn.btn-dark.description-btn 
          h3 #活动详情
        a(href="amc.amtee.updates.html").white.btn.btn-dark.events-btn             
          h3 #近期更新
        :markdown
          AMCISA会员们，久违的 “ AMTee会服设计比赛 ” 2016年重磅来袭!!
          我们再次号召极富艺术才华的会员们，以AMTee为画布，尽情挥洒你们的创作与想象力，为AMCISA设计更具张力的徽标～
          AMTee一件，创意无限，敬请踊跃参与!!
          
          请点击上方“活动规则”以了解设计比赛之细则。


        a(href="http://amcisa.org/gh/amtee.html").btn.btn-dark.btn-lg
            h3 我要参赛!

      .col-md-3

    .container.grey-bg.full-pg#description-label
      .row
        .col-md-3
        .col-md-6
          h1.border-bottom-light 活动详情
        .col-md-3
      .row
        .col-md-4
        .col-md-5.align-left
          h2
            span.fa.fa-fw.fa-clock-o.red &nbsp;
            | 上传作品开放日期 : 
            //- Replace the following date with event date
            | 28th December 2015  

          h2 
            span.fa.fa-fw.fa-calendar.yellow &nbsp;
            | 截止日期 : 
            //- Replace the following time with event time
            | 15th February 2016

        .col-md-3

block script
  script(type='text/javascript').
    $(document).ready(function(){
      pageScrollTo("description");
      return false;
    })